msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up wrong livelihood,"

msgctxt "an10.119:10.4"
msgid "micchāājīvā paccorohati."
msgstr "they descend from wrong livelihood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an10.119:11.1"
msgid "… ‘Micchāvāyāmassa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "‘Wrong effort has a bad result"

msgctxt "an10.119:11.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti."
msgstr "in both this life and the next.’"

