msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up wrong knowledge,"

msgctxt "an10.119:14.4"
msgid "micchāñāṇamhā paccorohati."
msgstr "they descend from wrong knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an10.119:15.1"
msgid "… ‘Micchāvimuttiyā kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "‘Wrong freedom has a bad result"

msgctxt "an10.119:15.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti."
msgstr "in both this life and the next.’"

msgctxt "an10.119:15.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya micchāvimuttiṃ pajahati;"
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up wrong freedom,"

msgctxt "an10.119:15.4"
msgid "micchāvimuttiyā paccorohati."
msgstr "they descend from wrong freedom."

msgctxt "an10.119:15.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hotī”ti."
msgstr "This is the ceremony of descent in the training of the noble one.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an10.119:16.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññathā, bho gotama, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī, aññathā ca pana ariyassa "
"vinaye paccorohaṇī hoti."
msgstr ""
"“The ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is quite different from "
"that observed in the training of the noble one."

msgctxt "an10.119:16.2"
msgid ""
"Imissā ca, bho gotama, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇiyā brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī "
"kalaṃ nāgghati soḷasiṃ."
msgstr ""
"And, Master Gotama, the ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is not "
"worth a sixteenth part of a master of the ceremony of descent observed in "
"the training of the noble one."

msgctxt "an10.119:16.3"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! …"

msgctxt "an10.119:16.4"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.119:16.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
